				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\varphi }_{B0}=-0.3$$\end{document} eV leads the higher the open-circuit voltage (VOC) and PCE. In the next step, a screening-based approach has been employed to study the cell efficiency over a wide range of defect densities. Two categorized defect types including benign defects (Nt<1016\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
